1. *Pročitaj* knjigu do kraja. (Read the book until the end.)
2. Molim te, da mi *pročitaš* ovaj tekst naglas. (Please read this text out loud to me.)
3. Ne mogu *pročitati* sitna slova bez naočara. (I can't read small letters without glasses.)
4. *Pročitao* sam ovu knjigu tri puta. (I have read this book three times.)
5. Da li si *pročitala* ovaj članak u novinama? (Have you read this article in the newspaper?)
6. Zaboravio sam *da pročitam* poruku koju si mi poslala. (I forgot to read the message you sent me.)
7. *Pročitajmo* zajedno ovaj pasus i pokušajmo da ga razumemo. (Let's read this paragraph together and try to understand it.)
8. Da li ćeš uspeti *da pročitaš* ovaj rukopis na starom jeziku? (Will you manage to read this manuscript in an old language?)